"2  (750 ml) bottles red wine","3 cups apricot nectar","2  small oranges, halved through stem end and cut lengthwise into thin slices","2  lemons, halved through stem end and cut lengthwise into thin slices","2  plums, halved through stem end, pitted and thinly sliced lengthwise","10  green grapes, halved lengthwise","3 cups plain seltzer or club soda","  Ice cubes for serving"